{"tid":35471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小別勝新婚 蔡少芬啜爆老公","createTime":"2016-12-12T06:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T06:03:18.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"790baa0b5102e452dd1f1ed7b20667bdd8e157d0","tid":35471,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"蔡少芬（Ada）老公張晉在澳洲拍完西片回港，兩公婆小別勝新婚，不忘晒恩愛。Ada在微博放閃啜爆老公，說是大女楚兒（湯圓）逼迫她們的，不過她也承認很享受。Ada在微博留言：「這是出自湯圓的手藝，是她指定的動作設計！信我&hellip;我們也是被逼的！（很樂意被逼的我，享受中）」。不過溫馨過後，正為無綫新劇《老表，畢業喇！》開工的Ada，傍晚時份就貼上在化妝間開餐照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/140148_4042ef4fb03a9791fd0a8c5108a08107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F140148_4042ef4fb03a9791fd0a8c5108a08107.jpg&h=fb467c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/140150_e44ab232374a27298fc1286b3fe5b201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F140150_e44ab232374a27298fc1286b3fe5b201.jpg&h=e28e653d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/12/140230_b270782ae3c749d1a89c922193f36cd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F140230_b270782ae3c749d1a89c922193f36cd6.jpg&h=b80b48cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/py75UVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpy75UVg.jpg&h=3f679576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Ada同老公甜蜜到不得了，去楊怡同羅仲謙的婚禮，自己都忍唔住啜埋一份。</span>"}]}